    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Clausia lubbockii Claparède, 1863, female. A, habitus, dorsal; B, egg sac; C, genital somite and abdomen, dorsal; D, right caudal ramus, dorsal; E, rostrum and antennule, dorsal; F, antenna; G, labrum; H, mandible; I, maxillule, posterior. Scale bars: A, 0.5 mm; B, 1 mm; C, 0.1 mm; D–F, 0.05 mm; G–I, 0.02 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5264673/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5264677>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Clausia lubbockii Claparède, 1863, female. A, maxilla; B, maxilliped; C, leg 1; D, leg 2; E, leg 3; F, leg 5. Scale bars: A–E, 0.02 mm; F, 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5264677/files/figure.png" ;
